- Restkit is an data synchronization framwork to
  + perform HTTP request
  + JSON serialization
  + JSON mapping & parsing
- Restkit is not popular these day, we can use this instead
  + perform HTTP request: Alamofire
  + JSON serialization: NSJSONSerialization or Alamofire
  + JSON mapping & parsing: Mantle or ObjectMapper
  + Core data synchronization and mapping from/to custom domain model can be taken by Mantle
